{"tid":1001848,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周柏豪玻璃杯逝世7周年 大批網民湧入原Post悼念","createTime":"2019-01-30T12:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T13:19:02.000Z","uid":179908,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c8832fbb2cba536984381d844d99a90a35b8f68a","tid":1001848,"uid":179908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:52:02.000Z","msg":"7年前的今天，有一件令人傷心欲絕的事發生，就是周柏豪跌碎了他最心愛的玻璃杯！因傷心過度，周柏豪體內的文人氣質在絕景時爆發出來，「呀」一聲就進化成「大文豪」，為玻璃杯拍下遺照，更留它寫下百多字的悼文，令到文壇徒此多事！<br />\n<br />\n周柏豪玻璃杯逝世7周年<br />\n<br />\n這一宗文壇大事發生於2012年1月30日，原來不知不覺已經7年，7年間柏豪奪得了叱吒唱作人金獎、男歌手金獎，在紅館發過2場演唱會，連唱片公司都轉了，加入大台和胡鴻鈞爭1哥位置&hellip;&hellip;生活如此忙碌，相信柏豪是不想停下來想起已經粉碎了的玻璃杯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH9qqcX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTH9qqcX.png&h=bd808094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信各位網民都坐日曆上記低了如此偉大的事件，因為7周年的今天竟然有大批網民回到事發post留言，除了關心柏豪外，有心人還想看看玻璃碎的近況。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7205204e8a13ee2731b30809e3576a2f157833","tid":1001848,"uid":5188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:53:14.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f08e26766548a091fbf6e9a67d38d4a9dee2cce","tid":1001848,"uid":179908,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUs7Dzp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUs7Dzp.png&h=c033e0cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d04ab6294525c9ea0d05c1d316633549305490","tid":1001848,"uid":1067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"小智棄養周柏豪二十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b20273765c4ecfe0b43e38ecc572b96aa2b8d6","tid":1001848,"uid":37524,"like